description: Do you feel like a jack of all trades, master of none? Me too. I have always wanted a space to record or display my various creative endeavors or adventures, but a social media page doesnâ€™t quite cut it. There are different outlets, such as music, resin art, or crochet projects which I would like to display in a more organized portfolio. For my startup project I am going to create a personal portfolio website which can function as a sort of blog as well. I will add functionality so that those who visit the website can create a profile and leave likes, comments, and messages. This way, they can leave feedback or ask for details on a certain project or excursion.
